Jaws equal, mouth terminal. Maxilla reaching vertical through anterior margin of orbit. Premaxillary teeth in two rows (Fig. 4). Outer row with 2(1), 3*(7), 4(13), or 5(4) tricuspid teeth. Inner row with 5 tetra- to pentacuspid teeth. Maxilla with 5 or 6(2) tri- to tetracuspid teeth. Dentary with 4 large, penta- to heptacuspid teeth followed by 11-12(2) smaller unito tricuspid teeth (
Fig. 3
).
